Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后继续杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我一直在杀她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永无止境地追杀她 无数次 无数次 无数次…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说你已经习惯了杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样只会不断侵蚀你的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是只有我才能做得到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 真那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战中止 回收至世界之树
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:49.20,yinzhu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(528.344,435)}Fraxinus
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道 你听得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道 你在这儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受伤了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 很痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的伤没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 那走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续约会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我黄豆面包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰克福面包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小笼包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十香 我手头没有钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 令音把魔法卡片借给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这不是白吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令音告诉了我 狂三和真那的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须阻止狂三像这样无止境地杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我却没有自信面对这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂三虽然是精灵 但是和十香和四纟乃迥异
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有那回事喔 士道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂三和我没有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有士道陪伴着我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是士道拯救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像今天这样士道邀请我约会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我展现了这个世界温暖的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:06:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有士道 我可能会变得和现在的狂三一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说我和狂三有不同的话 那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身边有没有人伸出援助之手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 十香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你让我明白了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不害怕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是会有点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 士道就由我来守护
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让我受到鼓舞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道 能让此刻多停留一会儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道同学 你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五河士道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚到学校就这么嚣张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法直视
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 现在能别打扰士道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法直视
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还真是吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为士道同学今天肯定是要请假的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂三
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说了很奇怪的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不让你杀人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不让真那杀你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.78,0:08:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道同学 就让我来试验一下你说的话究竟是真是假
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塔托斯克机关
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:10.21,yinzhu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ratatoskr
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.66,0:08:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你和哥哥在那种组织里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你调查了这么多呢 目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五河士道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让赤手空拳的哥哥去和精灵会面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经失去作为妹妹的资格了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的事情 就由我来接手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑 想叫我把士道托付给DEM社这样的恶德企业吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:35.54,yinzhu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(677.531,435)}Deus ex machina
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么知道这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太小瞧我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了拉塔托斯克以外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:41.04,yinzhu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ratatoskr
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,供给显现装置给世界上的军队和警察的军事企业
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是从那里来到AST的公司职员对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:08:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还未能确认时崎狂三是否下课了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是 她有没有偷听到我们的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 琴里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就由我来做领航员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上进行解析
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我们是恶德企业 我可不能置若罔闻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里给予了失去记忆的我以存在的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个让我感激不尽的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是认真的？居然被弄到那种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对崇宫真那用过的杯子内所提取到的体液进行了一番调查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的全身被施加了大量的魔力处理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计只能活不到十年了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.18,0:09:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:10:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 来禅高中内出现了强烈的灵波反应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是时崎狂三
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广域结界 是使范围内的人类变得衰弱的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂三她为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.39,0:10:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十香 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 只是觉得身体实在太沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只有我没事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时封印十香和四纟乃的灵力于体内的你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像受到了精灵的加护一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种状况下 能够正常活动的人只有你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.58,0:10:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道同学 听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果找我有事的话 就请到屋顶上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽快来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十香 你在这里休息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:10:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我会去拯救她的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,识别 AST 鸢一折纸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基础显现装置 启动承认
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎 等你很久了 士道同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你使用了紧急着装吧 状况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常危险 请求支持
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.53,0:11:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折纸同学 这么着急是要去哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时崎狂三
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 此路不通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道 士道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要一个人去 士道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体动起来 动起来 动起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊 十香同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂三 你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒吧 蚀时之城
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦踏上我的影子就会被吸取时间的结界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间？那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的时间 也就是寿命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天使拥有惊人的力量 但是相应地要消耗大量的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此时不时地 需要从外部进行充能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人不幸都是我可爱的饵料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 只有士道是与众不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 我为了与你合为一体  为了直接吃掉你才来到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是你的目标的话 没必要做那么过分的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吃掉你之前 我想让你收回今天早上的发言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拯救我之类的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:14:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道同学 就因为这个理由而做这些事的我是不是很可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可恨吧 明白了我是不值得怜悯的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所 以 说 请把那句话收回
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这样做的话 让我把这个结界解开也是可以的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对 快点嘛 要是错过时机的话可就无法挽回了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你解开结界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 收回那句话我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我厌烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.96,0:14:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白这个声音代表着什么意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空间震警报？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非时崎狂三她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能自发地引起作为突发灾害的空间震吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不打算收回那句话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果空间震发生了的话 失去知觉的学生们会如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小士 狂三的精神状态正在发生变化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来很有可能会袭击你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 狂三 你说过你的目的是吃掉我对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让空间震停下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就从这里跳下去自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己当人质？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是幼稚的想法 你要是敢跳就跳一个我看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信 你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:16:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这说明我有作为人质的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能请你停下空间震吗 另外把这结界也解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则我咬舌自尽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 还有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有要求?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂三 你还能再一次重来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还执着于那…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.04,0:16:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来是未知的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也许会喜欢上那种理所应当的和平生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则你也不会这么享受和我的约会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的 我能让你做到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的罪孽需要用一生去偿还
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:17:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是狂三 无论你错得多深 都无法动摇我要拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.26,0:17:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道 我 真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以的喔 被花言巧语迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.99,0:17:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂三
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.22,0:17:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好 我明白了 请安息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂三 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候的我可能太年轻了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不要再兜圈子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:18:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 又是千钧一发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都这么厉害 真不愧是真那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能这么轻易地劈开我的灵装
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我还不能这么轻易地被你杀掉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻刻帝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:18.83,yinzhu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Zaphkiel
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四之弹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:24.92,yinzhu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,dalet
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人瞠目的恢复能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是喔 是让时间倒流
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧来吧 让我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意 我会一如既往地杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是绝对无法杀掉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你喉咙开始割裂你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一之弹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aleph
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真那
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七之弹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:15.82,yinzhu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zayin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真那
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂三
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真那
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.60,0:19:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 大家都到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂三 竟然在战斗中逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.12,0:19:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再让你跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 人家好怕怕呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.96,0:19:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我一个弱女子 竟然这么多人欺负
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 今天我是动真格的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:19:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs(28)}怎么样 开心吧 一起来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的过去 我的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在各个时间轴上的我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗 杀不尽我的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 让我们一起完结吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了 为了让你无法再蛊惑我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得将绝望铭刻到你心中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.18,0:20:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次可真的会有好多人死去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空间震发生时如果遇到同样规模的震动 会被抵消
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.00,0:21:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道 把它稍微还给我下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.56,0:21:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焦灼吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灼烂歼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:43.47,yinzhu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Camael
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.48,0:21:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 开始我们的战争吧
